name: Two generations Dialogue
description:
This work represents a traditional rickshaw vehicle which metamorphosed into a rickshaw pulled by a motorcycle due to the changing times. Location for taking the painting object is Jogjakarta, Indonesia. 

Watercolor painting, size 97 X 56 cm, Produced 2 May 2 2018, Dimensions 1476 x 868 

Personal use only. For commercial use please contact me through social media. twitter: @ramdaniguruh instagram: Guruh Ramdani
